        "content": "# Generate short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive for Shorts\n\n**Pattern:** Video Production · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nGenerate short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive for Shorts. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual shorts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse XLSX Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Google Sheets → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to video production without manual effort\n- Anyone automating shorts in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
